data.description: One of the nicest properties in the entire community! This home is fantastic inside and out! Just one look at the images and you can tell this one is special! Wonderful floor plan with beautiful features throughout. You will love the architecture in this home with 9 foot ceilings, vaulted areas along with art niches to show off your treasures! The size of all the rooms is very impressive and unique to this home! The rear yard is truly an oasis that you can access from the glassed in Arizona room or from the Master bedroom. You will enjoy the overall appeal of the rear yard with separate areas to relax with a book or entertain your guests. Located in the East Valleys best value in gated 55 plus living!!
